{"tid":1534263,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"教你用經濟學角度去長期抗爭","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:29:27.000Z","uid":272805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9446ce3a40e4c7b37ebf695bd79b246c1fd6c9f","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"我地首先要明白人係一個好懶的生物，如果我地要長期抗爭，一定要利用一d方法去幫我地繼續落去。<br />\n<br />\n經濟學有個概念叫Nudge，中文叫推力，簡單來講就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改變我地預設的選擇</span></span>去達至一個好的結果。<br />\n<br />\n現實例子包括<br />\n強姦金入面的預設投資基金<br />\n有d國家會預設你會捐器官，你想唔捐可以取消番<br />\n健康食物放當眼位會增加買的機率<br />\n宜家流行的訂閱制度 等等<br />\n<br />\n我地可以用番同樣方法去幫我地抗爭，例如<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">搞定期轉帳俾星火/612，唔好記得或有事先課金<br />\n用電話較鬧鐘提醒自己每月某日要罷買<br />\n怕跳閘的朋友可以改變習慣坐巴士<br />\n電腦首頁set 蘋果/立場 <br />\n電視機較定一開就係港台/viutv <br />\n等等<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家有其他諗法都可以提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4beeffdb37dae7438dae31169d28e507e85df2","tid":1534263,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccebc6ff2e3f0838b1ba73b52548f0a568832640","tid":1534263,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=fad51e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 908都要照上街<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"54df605eeac4668896862069a78525019b128df4","tid":1534263,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"07fe6f17fe9a27f3903075872c798a403d68ea59","tid":1534263,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"出糧轉美金"},{"pid":"cb33d805d64238312da57522474fb2323159ea92","tid":1534263,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:05:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"faaa33fe2f8f2fa7dbf1bc5bcd508de544ab2c0b","tid":1534263,"uid":301692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"［現在公開可能な情報］9月到底抱咩心態去做人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跪求一閱"},{"pid":"6b18574fd674e250faa288794672545283ffcfb0","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07fe6f17fe9a27f3903075872c798a403d68ea59","tid":1534263,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"出糧轉美金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用電腦提自己要禁錢/轉美金"},{"pid":"7724c99abb3fe18b44d0fa936dc3a6d3885a8e4e","tid":1534263,"uid":101903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dacc68e7e63344bc23243c6d5087a1039fee6c7","tid":1534263,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d21e3ff4b2a219a1d3feb3cb4db4bdb3aaaa6a30","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"人係好懶，長期抗爭要靠習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fcefed84e7be727bb5708daffbc693ca3863fc","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"可以諗下買九巴月票<br />\n只少未來30日都唔會坐港鐵先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b451368b1ef0a4514a71dfddcf529d91be679ca2","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"外國有研究指選舉前問人投唔投票會增加投票率<br />\n選舉前記得問哂所有人投唔投票（藍絲除外）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04a76ffb93a145561c1529f1c33a1f7dbdcaed8","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n831"},{"pid":"8299b1d6b7c2faf2aa348daf105013d890029a7e","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n831"},{"pid":"467889a567d5d4065ebbac84ccbe8eb2f4b9d0b5","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"9f566921c675d85acbada290b5697e29b12323e4","tid":1534263,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28ad1c0977ffd951549099822458b1742153e426","tid":1534263,"uid":103374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"Delete 咗手機入面淘寶支那寶微信先啦，<br />\n呢樣嘢都唔做唔好話自己反送中"},{"pid":"753bae011b7a7b02e34cb3bca528ce7f1884d6df","tid":1534263,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"831"}]}